             (police-constable, G 122). I took the prisoner, and have the property.</p>
               <p>WILLIAM DAVEY. This is my property - he said it was his first offence, and he hoped I would forgive him.</p>
               <p>The prisoner handed in a petition for a lenient sentence, stating this to be his first offence.</p>
